task.summary: Default task
Optimizer based on apache maths + small test.
Fixing an error in computing log likelihood function.
Further fixes - for instance in classification algorithm.
Some new methods for the purpose of testing train and test sets.
Little refactoring.
Evaluating mesh of hyper parameters implemented.
Some files with mesh evaluation added. Kalman filter implemented, not tested.
Some code testing kalman filter in object tracking task, some improvements/fixes.
Unscented kalman filter implemented - not tested yet.
Gp regression reimplemented.
Computing derivatives of log likelihood w.r.t hyperparams.
Optimization of gp regression hyperparams.
Changed kernel func definition.
Since now, noise optimization can be turned off.
Some refactoring, new dataset test for gp regression.
GPOptimizer implemented - not tested, lot of code refactoring.
GPOptimizer improved a lot and tested.
Added spring IoC container for testing purposes.
Some code refactoring involved with optimization.
Many improvements in ukf algorithm.
GP UnscentedKalmanFilter implemented.
GP Ukf with kernel hyper params optimization - not tested yet.
Gp Ukf with hyper param optimization tested, ukf test is enriched with some stuff.
Class Testing sinusoidal ssm with ukf.
Testing Ssm much more improved.
ukf transform params mesh evaluator implemented.
Implemented nll computation and optimization w.r.t to it.
Removed unnecessary optimizer involved with gp predictor - hyperparams optimization, gp-ukf test in SsmTest class.
Changed logging a bit, ssm tests are run on the same samples.
GP-UKF since now with UT-params learning.
GP-UKF since now has to generate latent samples from ssm model, they are not passed to it as before.
Refactoring of gp predictor interface - removed ambiguity of hyper params passing. Co2 prediction implemented.
Spring context file complemented with co2 kernel.
Svm regression implemented with jlibsvm library, hyper params optimization in GPO algorithm.
Svm regression with general kernel func.
Improving SE kernel - length scales vector length equals to data dimension.
Breeze updated to version 0.8.1
